@startuml
title UC008 - Control Flow Diagram (Add Car Park to Favourites)
start

:1. User selects car park to add to favourites;
:2. Submit request to add to favourites;

if (3. Are car park details valid?) then (yes)
  :4. Add car park to favourites;
  
  if (5. Is car park already in favourites?) then (yes)
    :6. Display "This car park is already in your favourites" message;
     -1. [Retry] Return to car park select
  stop
  else (no)
    :7. Confirm addition to user's profile;
    :8. Add car park to favourites list;
    :9. Display confirmation message ("Car park added to favourites");
  endif
  
else (no)
  :10. Display "Car park is no longer available" message;
  -1. [Retry] Return to car park select
  stop
endif

stop
@enduml
